{"word":"G5237 - ὑπερείδω - hypereídō - hoop-er-i'-do - Wink at","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπερείδω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hypereídō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-er-i'-do</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Wink at</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - காண்"},{"paragraph":"to overlook"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5228 - ὑπέρ - hypér - hoop-er'/5228\">G5228</a> and <a href=\"#/G1492 - εἴδω - eídō - i'-do/1492\">G1492</a>; to <i>overlook</i>, that is, <i>not punish:</i> - wink at.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}